{"tid":678370,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"食評：元朗 Flavour Kitchen","createTime":"2018-05-26T04:34:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-27T04:39:53.000Z","uid":181719,"like":6,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6f698d549c84ff1e88ceb2dd5fcac055056ced55","tid":678370,"uid":181719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T04:34:09.000Z","msg":"最近發覺 tea time 去食西餐係一個幾抵嘅玩法 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為一樣嘅食物，西餐茶市同晚市嘅價差通常大過其他菜式好多。好似呢間野，下午茶鋸扒加燒春雞2個餐，170蚊到，晚市食返一樣嘅野，一倍價錢有多。<br />\n<br />\n牛扒叫咗7成熟，其實真係煎得幾靚仔。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/26/123002_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F26%2F123002_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=24c102fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n食落肉味唔係話好香濃，但係絕對對得住價錢喎。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/26/123030_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F26%2F123030_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=17a4ae8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n燒春雞其實燒得幾唔錯嘅，火候好，但係賣相就有點兒肉酸。呢個都其次，最大問題係唔夠味。始終一般人對燒雞嘅期望都係惹味行先，呢隻真係清淡咗啲，自己加鹽啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/26/123044_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F26%2F123044_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=d0567280&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/26/123056_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F26%2F123056_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=7a31d16d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n兩碟都係配薯條，炸得幾金黃香脆而唔燶，如果粗啲就會更好喇。<br />\n<br />\n湯同沙律係基本野啦，冇乜驚喜。最後要講兩杯餐飲，其實一開始係比「餐飲配特式加啡」個招牌吸引入黎，結果叫咗一杯cappuccino 一杯mocca，都係大路野，都係冇乜驚喜。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/26/123117_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F26%2F123117_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=3c40ae4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/26/123125_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F26%2F123125_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=0f25023c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/26/123139_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F26%2F123139_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=95d854d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/26/123149_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F26%2F123149_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=4496c6d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過總括黎講，都係抵食嘅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3542e1db9145f853ead0414addd8bba637330c3c","tid":678370,"uid":16087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T18:23:37.000Z","msg":"好似好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"478b73d6877283c32cbef33a3a9ee7f2739b9b62","tid":678370,"uid":22112,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T18:25:17.000Z","msg":"邊撚度黎?"},{"pid":"ac89bbefaef329b533238ce1c09811d79d436a0e","tid":678370,"uid":47945,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"478b73d6877283c32cbef33a3a9ee7f2739b9b62","tid":678370,"uid":22112,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"cited